  "title": "Digitalization Engineer / IT Systems Engineer (Factory & Engineering Support)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Digitalization Engineer / IT Systems Engineer (Factory & Engineering Support)</strong></h3><p>Manage and develop your internal digital systems.</p><p>Support ERP/MRP implementation for production, inventory, QC, project tracking.</p><p>Digitalize workshop processes (tablet forms, barcode tracking, material traceability).</p><p>Build internal tools/automation for documentation and compliance.</p><p>Automated calculation tools (using your engineers' formulas).</p><p>Document generators (ASME data sheets, material traceability, welding logs).</p><p>Workflow automation (Python, Excel apps, web dashboards).</p><p>Simple thermal or mechanical calculation utilities (with guidance).</p><p>Automate processes</p><p>Improve productivity</p><p>Digitalize documentation</p><p>Build internal tools</p>",
